column2: SELECT    m.name as name, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,     m.objid AS HSC_objid, m.imag_psf AS HSC_imag_psf,    m.imag_psf_err AS HSC_imag_psf_err,       n.objID, n.distance,    p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2,         p.psfMag_g, p.psfMagErr_g,     p.psfMag_r, p.psfMagErr_r,     p.psfMag_i, p.psfMagErr_i,     p.psfMag_z, p.psfMagErr_z,        p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r,     p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z    into HSC_star_DR1#    FROM MyDB.HSC_sql_query_star_ra_dec  AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objID = p.objID        WHERE         p.clean = #     --  AND (p.flags_g & dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) = #  --AND (p.flags_r & dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) = #  -- AND (p.flags_i & dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) = #  -- AND(  --    (# < p.psfMag_g-p.cModelMag_g AND p.psfMag_g-p.cModelMag_g < #)   --   OR      --  (# < p.psfMag_r-p.cModelMag_r AND p.psfMag_r-p.cModelMag_r < #)     -- OR        --(# < p.psfMag_i-p.cModelMag_i AND p.psfMag_i-p.cModelMag_i < #)  --)
